  "Find the derivative of sin(3x) using the chain rule.": "",
  "-3sin(3x)": "",
  "3sin(3x)": "",
  "cos(3x)": "",
  "3cos(3x)": "",
  "d/dx[sin(3x)] = cos(3x) * 3 = 3cos(3x) by the chain rule. The derivative of the outer function (cos) times the derivative of the inner function (3).": "",
  "Evaluate the integral of sin(x) dx from 0 to pi.": "",
  "pi": "",
  "2": "",
  "Integral = [-cos(x)] from 0 to pi = -cos(pi) - (-cos(0)) = -(-1) + 1 = 1 + 1 = 2.": "",
  "What is the derivative of arcsin(x)?": "",
