  "-2, particularly regarding below according to conventional analysis": "",
  "2pi (the circumference), particularly regarding does according to": "",
  "Integral from 0 to 2pi of sin(x) dx = [-cos(x)] from 0 to 2pi = -cos(2pi) + cos(0) = -1 + 1 = 0. The positive area above the x-axis exactly cancels the negative area below.": "",
