  "0 degrees per hour": "",
  "15 degrees per hour": "",
  "-15pi/12 ≈ -3.93 degrees per hour": "",
  "T'(t) = 15 * (pi/12) * cos(pi*t/12). At t = 6: T'(6) = (15pi/12)cos(pi/2) = (15pi/12)(0) = 0. At 6 AM, the temperature is at its maximum (35°C) and momentarily not changing.": "",
  "The area under one arch of y = sin(x) (from x = 0 to x = pi) is:": "",
